OL,3,CWho are the North Wests richest people
OL,4,Cand how did they make their money?
OL,6,FLancashire couple Richard and Debbie
OL,7,FNuttall, now find themselves among the
OL,8,FNorth West's wealthiest people.
OL,10,FBut the richest people in our region
OL,11,Fare not just millionaires, they are
OL,12,Fbillionaires.
OL,14,FThe brothers from Blackburn were
OL,15,Fbrought up in a terrace house and as
OL,16,Fteenagers worked at their parents
OL,17,Fpetrol station. They bought their
OL,18,Ffirst petrol station in 2001 and have
OL,19,Fsince made their millions by building
OL,20,Fpetrol forecourt firm EG Group.
