OL,6,FThere are more than 1,100 B&M shops
OL,7,Facross the country. The three brothers
OL,8,Fhave offloaded shares worth more than
OL,9,F#910 million since taking the discount
OL,10,Fretailer onto the stock market in
OL,11,F2014. Their remaining 6.98% holding is
OL,12,Fnow worth #390.2 million.
OL,14,FSimon Nixon dropped out of University
OL,15,Fand set up a price comparison website
OL,16,Fthat would later become
OL,17,FMoneysupermarket.
OL,19,FHe made more than #700 million from
